name: Paper Doll Blocks
description:
This set of 3 jumbo 2" blocks makes the perfect eco-friendly gift for the modern baby. These chunky blocks feature six vintage paper doll images: three girls and three boys. Simply turn the blocks to create different dolls.

{Details} 
❉3 blocks measuring 2" each
❉Each block is hand-sanded and sepia-inked to achieve a vintage look & feel.
❉This set arrives sweetly packaged ready for gifting

{Safety} 
All materials used to make tiny giraffe blocks are eco-friendly and non-toxic. The wood is untreated and chemical-free, and the blocks are finished with non-toxic, water-based sealant for durability. Not intended as a teething toy.
